com.ibm.lang.management

Class ProcessingCapacityNotificationInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.lang.management.ProcessingCapacityNotificationInfo

  • public class ProcessingCapacityNotificationInfo
extends Object
    Encapsulates the details of a DLPAR notification emitted by a OperatingSystemMXBean when the available processing capacity changes. Specifically, this notification indicates that the value returned by OperatingSystemMXBean.getProcessingCapacity() has changed.
    Since:
    1.5
